{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_08_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 麻奈ちゃんと一緒に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n一緒に来てくれてありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nthank you for coming with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、本当に良かったの？　買い出しだけじゃなくて\n遊びにまで付き合ってもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ are you sure it’s okay? Not just helping with the shopping‚\nbut also hanging out with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣とすずは、大会でも頑張っていたからな\nたまにはいいかと思ったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you and Suzu worked hard for the tournament‚\nso I thought it would be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1999996821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "はぐれないように手繋ごっか？\nえへへ、やったー！　でも、人が一杯だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Want to hold hands so we don’t get separated?\nEhehe‚ yay! There are so many people!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4666663487
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8333330154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことは、すずとやりなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Go do that with Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8333330154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "え～？\n{user}さんとも繋ぎたかったのにな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~?\nBut I wanted to hold hands with {user}-san too~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8333332697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4000017165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そういえばここのショッピングモール\n麻奈ちゃんと遊びに来たことがあるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Now that I think about it‚ I came to this shopping mall\nto hang out with Mana-chan before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2333350498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈に付き合うのは大変じゃなかったか？\nふわふわ飛び回るから、ついて行くのも苦労したろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wasn’t it hard to keep up with Mana?\nShe’s always flitting about‚ it must’ve been hard to follow her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0333350498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.4666709263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はすっごい楽しかったよ？　あ、でも\n麻奈ちゃんが{user}さんのこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was super fun for me? Ah‚ but‚\nMana-chan said something about you‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0000042597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "「一緒に買い物に行くと、す～ぐクタクタに\nなっちゃうの」……なんて言ってたかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“He gets tired out so easily when we go shopping together.”\nProbably that's what she said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666709263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4333347956
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がアクティブ過ぎるんだよ\n壁とか床とか、平気ですり抜けて飛んで行くからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana’s just too active.\nShe phases through walls and floors and flies around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666681289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "他にも一杯話してくれたよ？　デートした時は\n一日中一緒にいたから！　例えば～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She told me a lot of other stories‚ too. Like when you guys went on a date‚\nyou were together all day! For example~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8999968846,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6800.000318000002,
          "startTime": 78.6999972026
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.2499968846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ここはペットショップか～\n見て見て、麻奈ちゃん！　ワンちゃんが一杯だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a pet shop~.\nLook‚ look‚ Mana-chan! So many puppies!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7999902726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5333230973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "この柴犬が……{user}さんに似てる？\nほんとだ、優しそうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This Shiba Inu… reminds me of {user}-san! Don’t you think so?\nIt does! It looks so gentle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9666564306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2166564306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "ワンちゃんを見ながら、どの子が一番\n{user}さんに似てるか話し合ったっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We used to look at all the puppies\nand discuss which one looked most like {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4333230973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.6999785742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに優勝は最初に見つけた柴犬だったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first Shiba Inu we saw was the winner!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6999785742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8666447323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺は犬に似てるのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I look like a dog…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8666447323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、見て！　あのお化け屋敷\nちょうど麻奈ちゃんと遊びに来た時もやってた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ look! That haunted house!\nIt was here when we came to hang out with Mana-chan too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0333113989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3499780656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、イベントスペースでお化け屋敷をやってるんだ！\n……あれ？　もしかして麻奈ちゃん、お化け屋敷苦手？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh~‚ they’re having a haunted house at the event space!\n…Huh? Could it be that you’re scared of haunted houses‚ Mana-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5666447323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.5666447323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ～、遊園地のお化け屋敷には\n{user}さんと入ったことあるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really~? You went to the haunted house\nat the amusement park with {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4999780656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1333164852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？\n麻奈ちゃん、なんか照れてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nMana-chan‚ why is your face red?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4999831518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.6833164852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてもごまかされちゃったんだけど\n麻奈ちゃんとお化け屋敷で、何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried to ask‚ but she just brushed it off…\nDid something happen between you and Mana-chan at the haunted house?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9666498185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　ま、まぁ……うん……\nでも、幽霊になってもお化けが怖いって変な話だよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? W-well… Yeah…\nBut it’s weird that she’s still scared of ghosts even after becoming one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9666498185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.9333164852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、顔赤いよ？",
      "translations": {
